headline.main: FLIERS RAKE BURMA BASE; British Shoot Up Troop Bodies and Bomb Factories and Shipping

abstract: Burma action: RAF raids Jap troop positions, Maungdaw; hits rys, Ingin; blasts factories, Kyangin; attacks shipping, Irrawaddy River near Pagan, Pakokku-Mandalay area, Kanauung and Myanaung
